This is a minimal stack to test external applications using Cucumber, Capybara and MiniTest, compatible with ruby 1.8.7 and 1.9.2. It has some example steps on features/step_definitions/web_steps.rb in English and Portuguese to get you started.


Instructions

1 - Clone the project
2 - Go to the project root
3 - Run 'bundle install'
4 - Run 'cucumber'   
5 - Have fun! :)
